# Testing Standards

Read and follow the "Testing Standards" section in `CONTRIBUTING.md`.

Key rules: Vitest with explicit imports (no globals), `.js` extensions on source imports, no `any` in fixtures, no SDK mocking in unit tests, mapper tests are the priority for providers.
